TITLE: Example UDP Packet Size Calculation for JoinRoom Operation
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the byte-by-byte calculation of a JoinRoom operation packet size, including all protocol overhead from UDP/IP headers through operation parameters. Shows how a simple room join command requiring 8 bytes of payload results in a 74-byte total packet size.
