Operation header: 8 bytes
Total operation size: 22 bytes
eNet send command: 12 bytes
Total with command: 34 bytes
eNet package header: 12 bytes
Total Photon packet: 46 bytes
UDP/IP headers: 28 bytes
Final packet size: 74 bytes
```

