TITLE: Implementing Local Input with Quantum Callbacks
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement local input handling using Quantum callbacks in a MonoBehaviour.
SOURCE: https://github.com/xsampedro/quantum3_docs/blob/main/output/quantum3/manual/quantum-ecs/game-events.md#2025-04-23_snippet_26

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
public class LocalInput : MonoBehaviour {
  private DispatcherSubscription _pollInputDispatcher;
  private void OnEnable() {
    _pollInputDispatcher = QuantumCallback.Subscribe(this, (CallbackPollInput callback) => PollInput(callback));
  }
  public void PollInput(CallbackPollInput callback) {
    Quantum.Input i = new Quantum.Input();
    callback.SetInput(i, DeterministicInputFlags.Repeatable);
  }
  private void OnDisable(){
    QuantumCallback.Unsubscribe(_pollInputDispatcher);
  }
}
```

